To run tests do following:

1. Poll PHP unit stuff from following locations:
     git://github.com/sebastianbergmann/phpunit.git
     git://github.com/sebastianbergmann/php-code-coverage.git
     git://github.com/sebastianbergmann/php-file-iterator.git
     git://github.com/sebastianbergmann/php-token-stream.git
     git://github.com/sebastianbergmann/php-text-template.git
     git://github.com/sebastianbergmann/php-timer.git

2. Create ENV variable PHPUNIT with correct paths:
     export PHPUNITPATH="<PATH/TO/PHPUNIT>"
     export PHPUNIT="$PHPUNITPATH/phpunit:$PHPUNITPATH/php-code-coverage:$PHPUNITPATH/php-file-iterator:$PHPUNITPATH/php-token-stream:$PHPUNITPATH/php-text-template:$PHPUNITPATH/php-timer"

5. Execute tests:
     php -d include_path=".:$PHPUNIT" PHPUnitTests/AllTests.php